---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<section class="elected-section" id="elected-by-the-people">
  <div class="elected-bg">
    <div class="elected-pattern"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container elected-content">
    <span class="elected-label animate-in" data-i18n="meet.elected_label">Elected by the People</span>
    
    <h2 class="elected-headline animate-in" data-i18n="meet.elected_headline">
      A Grassroots Movement, Not a Machine Candidacy
    </h2>
    
    <div class="elected-narrative">
      <p class="elected-paragraph animate-in" data-i18n="meet.elected_p1">
        In 2019, Byron ran a grassroots campaign for Alderman of the 25th Ward. He committed to refuse political contributions from developers and big corporations - a commitment he has upheld to this day and beyond. Since taking office, any resident now can personally meet with Byron at his weekly Ward Night, and all residents can receive compassion, support, and city services from the devoted public servants who staff the 25th Ward office.
      </p>

      <p class="elected-paragraph animate-in" data-i18n="meet.elected_p2">
        In 2023, big money and the political establishment lined up against Byron. Byron took democratic establishment and corrupt Danny Solis all the way to the Illinois Supreme Court over his unethical campaign finance practices. The voters of the 25th Ward sent him back to City Hall.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="elected-paragraph elected-intro animate-in" data-i18n="meet.elected_p3">
      As an elected official, he used the power of his office to put the people's power into the institutions that needed it - under his leadership, change is happening.
    </p>

    <div class="achievements-grid">
      <div class="achievement-item animate-in">
        <div class="achievement-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="m3 9 9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
            <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="achievement-title" data-i18n="meet.achieve_housing_title">800+ Affordable Units</h3>
        <p class="achievement-desc" data-i18n="meet.achieve_housing_desc">
          Byron has preserved and created over 800 units of affordable housing across Chicago and as Chairman of the Committee on Housing and Real Estate, made Chicago the largest city to pass a $135 million dollar investment via the Green Social Housing Initiative, to build sustainable housing and help address the housing crisis in Illinois.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="achievement-item animate-in">
        <div class="achievement-icon">
          <!-- Door Open Icon -->
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M13 4h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14"/>
            <path d="M2 20h3"/>
            <path d="M13 20h9"/>
            <path d="M10 12v.01"/>
            <path d="M13 4.562v16.157a1 1 0 0 1-1.242.97L5 20V5.562a2 2 0 0 1 1.515-1.94l4-1A2 2 0 0 1 13 4.561Z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="achievement-title" data-i18n="meet.achieve_wardnight_title">Open Door, Every Week</h3>
        <p class="achievement-desc" data-i18n="meet.achieve_wardnight_desc">
          Every community member has the opportunity to speak directly with their elected official every Tuesday at the Ward Office - the accountability is a commitment.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="achievement-item animate-in">
        <div class="achievement-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/>
            <path d="M3.22 12H9.5l.5-1 2 4.5 2-7 1.5 3.5h5.27"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="achievement-title" data-i18n="meet.achieve_health_title">Community Services</h3>
        <p class="achievement-desc" data-i18n="meet.achieve_health_desc">
          The Pilsen Food Pantry has grown to serve more than ever. Perpetrators of heinous crimes are held accountable more often and public safety has become more possible for the community to organize for. A dental clinic accessible to the people was opened and a mental health clinic as well.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="achievement-item animate-in">
        <div class="achievement-icon">
          <!-- Megaphone Icon -->
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="m3 11 18-5v12L3 14v-3z"/>
            <path d="M11.6 16.8a3 3 0 1 1-5.8-1.6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="achievement-title" data-i18n="meet.achieve_fight_title">Standing Against the Powerful</h3>
        <p class="achievement-desc" data-i18n="meet.achieve_fight_desc">
          Property tax payers know that their elected official has voted against every single proposed property tax increase, and worked to fight for a statewide millionaire surcharge and wealth taxes on the billionaires. When Trump sent ICE to our communities, Byron faced them head on with the full weight of his office and his community ensuring that Bovino and other thugs were held accountable to the furthest extent possible in court.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="elected-call animate-in" data-i18n="meet.elected_call">
      Byron has changed what was possible in public service on the municipal level and he isn't stopping. We need him in Congress.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Family Closing -->
<section class="family-closing" id="family">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="family-grid">
      <div class="family-image-wrap animate-in">
        <img 
          src={`${base}/images/byron-family-triplets.jpg`} 
          alt="Byron with his wife Loreen and their triplets"
          class="family-image"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="family-text animate-in">
        <h3 class="family-headline" data-i18n="meet.family_headline">Rooted in Pilsen</h3>
        <p class="family-desc" data-i18n="meet.family_desc">
          Byron, and his wife Loreen, live in Pilsen with their little triplets (who attend public school), and their dog, Buster, and their two cats Dos and 三歲.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA Block -->
<section class="meet-cta-block">
  <div class="container meet-cta-content">
    <h2 class="meet-cta-headline animate-in" data-i18n="meet.cta_headline">Send an Unbought Organizer to Congress.</h2>
    <div class="meet-cta-buttons animate-in">
      <a href="#petition" class="btn btn-orange btn-massive" data-i18n="meet.cta_petition">Join the Petition Blitz</a>
      <a href="https://secure.actblue.com/donate/byronfor04web/" class="btn btn-cream" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-i18n="meet.cta_donate">Donate to the Movement</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Elected Section */
  .elected-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .elected-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--blue);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .elected-pattern {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0.04;
    background-image: 
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }

  .elected-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .elected-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--gold-soft);
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .elected-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--cream);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .elected-narrative {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .elected-paragraph {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .elected-paragraph:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .elected-intro {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-3xl);
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .achievements-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .achievement-item {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(251, 226, 186, 0.12);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    transition: background var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-default), transform var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-default);
  }

  .achievement-item:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .achievement-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); /* Visible bounding box on blue */
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 8px;
    transition: all var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-default);
  }

  .achievement-item:hover .achievement-icon {
    background: var(--orange);
    color: var(--white);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .achievement-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .achievement-desc {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .elected-call {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--gold-soft);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* Family Closing */
  .family-closing {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }

  .family-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .family-image-wrap {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .family-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .family-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .family-desc {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--gray-700);
  }

  /* CTA Block */
  .meet-cta-block {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 0 0 var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .meet-cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .meet-cta-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--blue);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .meet-cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .achievements-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .elected-headline {
      font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    }

    .family-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .family-image {
      height: 300px;
    }

    .meet-cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .meet-cta-buttons .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
